{"tid":1900623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙田男子家居隔離周街走 衞署拒理","createTime":"2020-02-27T10:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T11:30:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"724cf8ddcf20a2696e71eabdd7b9bfaf5b3b2134","tid":1900623,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200227/7U326BRVL2VJ3YKESYTPEWHG54/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200227%2F7U326BRVL2VJ3YKESYTPEWHG54%2F&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=9ac46bec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200227%2F7U326BRVL2VJ3YKESYTPEWHG54%2F&h=95f22fa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200227/7U326BRVL2VJ3YKESYTPEWHG54/</a><br />\n<br />\n沙田男子家居隔離周街走 衞署拒理<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200227/large/1582737295_829d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200227%2Flarge%2F1582737295_829d.jpg&h=dba2af13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n康文署強調西貢戶外康樂中心嚴禁營友賭博。簡明恩攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】繼前日深水埗黃金電腦商場一名租客擅自開舖後，沙田希爾頓中心一名男戶主亦被揭發在家居隔離14天期間多次外出。有區議員接獲居民求助後通知衞生署，署方竟稱人手不足，反着議員報警，男戶主昨傍晚疑再度外出，管理處報警求助，警方稱會就事件通知相關部門跟進。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：香港疫症地圖<br />\n<br />\n街坊通知管理處報警<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，男戶主一家四口居於希爾頓中心A座一中層單位。區議員衞慶祥向《蘋果》指，事主一家早前回鄉度歲，上周六從內地返港，原應在家隔離14天。但近日男戶主被居民發現多次外出：「據居民反映，呢位男戶主唔係離開屋企門口踏出走廊咁簡單，而係離開屋苑走咗出去」，街坊擔心病毒在社區傳播。<br />\n<br />\n衞慶祥接獲居民求助後，聯絡衞生署反映，要求署方派員處理，直至昨早衞生署回覆，但表示人手不足，着他再發現有人違反隔離令，可報警處理。據知，大廈管理處曾翻查大廈出入紀錄，證實涉事男戶主曾多次出入大廈，管理處致電對方交涉不果，惟有加強清潔有關樓層。<br />\n<br />\n昨傍晚時份，有街坊發現涉事男戶主再外出，通知管理處報警。警方指昨午5時30分接獲報案，指一名男子疑違反檢疫令，離開沙田正街3至9號希爾頓中心一單位，警到場並在上址發現該男子，警方會就事件通知相關部門。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭文輝"},{"pid":"5de20a3068fe14fccb464163b751b0b84c0e2b9c","tid":1900623,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:32:21.000Z","msg":"［行動po 推上熱門thx] 2月29日(六) 毋忘831半周年<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1900575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1900575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e0d0b51fdfabb3c61ddd259215e16854357e1382","tid":1900623,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"攬炒！！好！！！"},{"pid":"60c7b96eab58903d55d42c0e7f9a9c4d6c545654","tid":1900623,"uid":180293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:42:21.000Z","msg":"衛生署&gt;黑警&gt;其他部門&gt;<br />\n典型垃圾政府做野"},{"pid":"46dcafc6744af56193def5c1c5dd5c0043b6b4ad","tid":1900623,"uid":155598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:42:41.000Z","msg":"黑警：關我撚事呀"},{"pid":"270b31ea191f491f339782edf9ef1c3332d1cb63","tid":1900623,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:51:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f3ff694e6e216657c69f3a1de1f890319217b429","tid":1900623,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"好波"},{"pid":"5bcee8eac79844e0d01e9f6f4b1b2e9cfdb6eb97","tid":1900623,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:53:55.000Z","msg":"攬炒呢個責任交係你手上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470d8909de24038f0b34a7ec157da13d040126df","tid":1900623,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"手足黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d922edfc492584c4343efc2af6489393038a36f","tid":1900623,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"470d8909de24038f0b34a7ec157da13d040126df","tid":1900623,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:55:36.000Z","msg":"手足黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"又 bloc